The paper discusses privacy concerns related to big data analytics and proposes privacy by design strategies and privacy enhancing technologies to address these concerns. This makes it highly relevant to the computer security (cs.CR) and database (cs.DB) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses issues related to data provenance, access control, and policy enforcement, which are relevant to the cyber security (cs.CY), machine learning (cs.LG), and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
